---
title: Lamb Tikka Meatballs with Garlic Basmati Rice
description: Homemade meatballs are delicately spiced and tossed in luxurious tikka sauce for a weeknight dinner that's bursting with flavour! Fluffy basmati rice, sweet peppers and a final flourish of cilantro round out this delectable dish.
